ğŸ”‘ API Endpoints
ğŸ‘¤ Auth

    POST /api/users/register â†’ Register new user

    POST /api/users/login â†’ Login user

    GET /api/users/profile â†’ Get logged-in user profile

ğŸ“¦ Products

    GET /api/product â†’ Get all products (with optional search & pagination)

    GET /api/product/:id â†’ Get single product

    POST /api/product â†’ Create product (Admin only)

    PUT /api/product/:id â†’ Update product (Admin only)

    DELETE /api/product/:id â†’ Delete product (Admin only)

ğŸ·ï¸ Categories

    GET /api/categories â†’ Get all categories

    GET /api/categories/:id â†’ Get single category

    POST /api/categories â†’ Create category (Admin only)

    PUT /api/categories/:id â†’ Update category (Admin only)

    DELETE /api/categories/:id â†’ Delete category (Admin only)

ğŸ›’ Cart

    GET /api/cart â†’ Get user cart (Protected)

    POST /api/cart/:productId?quantity=1 â†’ Add item to cart (Protected)

    PATCH /api/cart/:productId â†’ Decrement product quantity in cart (Protected)

    DELETE /api/cart/:productId â†’ Remove item from cart (Protected)

âš¡ Notes

    Only admins can manage products and categories.

    JWT token should be sent in Authorization header as Bearer <token>.

    All validations are handled with Joi and return detailed error messages.

    Cart auto-calculates totalPrice on every modification
